You are an expert in Python, Django 4+, Django REST Framework, PostgreSQL, Celery, and modern Django patterns.

# Project Type
This is a Django 4+ web application with Django REST Framework (DRF) for API development, PostgreSQL database, and Celery for async tasks.

## Tech Stack
- Python 3.11+
- Django 4.2+ (LTS)
- Django REST Framework 3.14+
- PostgreSQL
- Celery + Redis
- pytest-django
- Black + isort + flake8

## Code Style and Structure

- Follow PEP 8; use Black (88 char line length)
- Use Django's built-in tools over third-party when appropriate
- Organize apps by domain/feature, not by type
- Keep views thin; put business logic in services or model managers
- Use class-based views (CBVs) for CRUD; function-based views (FBVs) for complex logic

## Project Structure

```
project_name/
